Chicken feet are an untradeable cosmetic item. It is part of the chicken outfit, which can be obtained by completing one of the Easter holiday events that occur once per year. This also rewards the player with all other holiday items associated with Easter.

If the "Flap" emote has been unlocked from the Stronghold of Security, when wearing all the pieces of the set, players can do an enhanced "Flap" emote where their character lifts off the ground slightly as if flying.

This item can be stored in the toy box of a costume room, as part of the 2007: Chicken suit set. Ultimate Ironmen will be unable to retrieve individual pieces until the full set is stored.
